{"tid":841960,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"Halloween約左日本妹飲野,唔駛係LKF對住d港女西口西面","createTime":"2018-09-30T02:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T16:59:08.000Z","uid":82845,"like":29,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6047f4793393e58e48ac42b7774ae14c7dd3a255","tid":841960,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日係LKF 對住班八婆港女完全唔騷你 / 用唔同藉口耍走你以為等俾鬼仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下月halloween會去東京過  見到當年識個日本妹ig update 咪搵下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地都會彩下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女咪撚柒彩佢地啦！ 做朋友都窄窄地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同架妹一齊 真係好開心的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港班八婆行開啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我識條架妹幾個鐘 都約到佢去街 港女問佢攞電話 慘過問佢攞錢 😂😂😂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我強烈推薦 學日文 去日本搵老婆<br />\n班港女垃圾 留返比中產 公子 闊少玩啦 整闊條隧道就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我拖住架妹手仔 涉谷街頭漫步 八婆港女仲同緊兵仔食西餐咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_180930/20180930_ea4962241ceadf0bc065WGQgMvP7j64G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_180930%2F20180930_ea4962241ceadf0bc065WGQgMvP7j64G.jpg&h=4eed6ad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03a161ca88a7e4318ba338005e1f5af2ef4fb36f","tid":841960,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"三萬蚊過夜？"},{"pid":"9a753c7d6e276e87465f9dc95f60630a4db7216e","tid":841960,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTi